<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Press Release: Launch of FitTrack Mobile App</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Introducing FitTrack: Your Ultimate Fitness Companion</h1>
        <p>Available Now on iOS and Android</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>We are thrilled to announce the launch of FitTrack, a revolutionary mobile app designed to help users achieve their health and fitness goals with ease and precision. FitTrack is now available for download on both iOS and Android platforms.</p>

        <h2>About FitTrack</h2>
        <p>FitTrack is more than just a fitness tracking app; it's your personal fitness companion. With FitTrack, users can effortlessly track their workouts, monitor their progress, and connect with a community of like-minded fitness enthusiasts. Our app offers personalized recommendations tailored to individual fitness goals and preferences, ensuring that every user gets the most out of their fitness journey.</p>

        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Comprehensive workout tracking</li>
            <li>Progress monitoring with detailed analytics</li>
            <li>Personalized fitness recommendations</li>
            <li>Community platform to connect with other users</li>
            <li>Available on both iOS and Android</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Target Audience</h2>
        <p>FitTrack is perfect for fitness enthusiasts of all levels, from beginners who are just starting their journey to seasoned athletes looking for advanced tracking capabilities. Our app caters to anyone who is passionate about maintaining and improving their health and fitness.</p>

        <div class="quote">
            <p>"At FitTrack, we believe that fitness should be accessible and personalized for everyone. Our app is designed to empower users to take control of their health and achieve their goals in a supportive environment." - <strong>CEO, FitTrack</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="quote">
            <p>"We are excited to bring a new level of innovation to the fitness industry with FitTrack. Our app is a game-changer for anyone looking to enhance their fitness journey." - <strong>Head of Product Development, FitTrack</strong></p>
        </div>

        <h2>Download FitTrack Today</h2>
        <div class="cta">
            <p>Don't wait any longer to start your fitness journey with FitTrack. Download the app today and take the first step towards a healthier you!</p>
            <p><a href="https://fittrackapp.com" target="_blank">Visit our website</a> | <a href="https://twitter.com/fittrackapp" target="_blank">Twitter</a> | <a href="https://facebook.com/fittrackapp" target="_blank">Facebook</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
```

In this press release, I've included a detailed overview of the app's features, its target audience, and a clear call-to-action encouraging readers to download the app. It also contains quotes from key stakeholders, including the CEO and Head of Product Development, as well as links to the app's website and social media pages. Adjust the links and quotes as necessary to fit your actual app and team.
